4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp that prepares students to master in-demand technologies like JavaScript and Python. Spanning 16+2 weeks, students attend classes three times a week with a maximum ratio of 1 instructor per 7 students. The program requires no prior coding experience, and learners can choose between English and Spanish for the curriculum. By the end of the bootcamp, participants develop and present their own projects, gaining valuable hands-on experience. Successful graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more details, visit the website: [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop